    <item>
      <title>野村称特朗普贸易禁令漏洞将削弱中国经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-banning-trade-loophole-will-cut-china-s-growth-nomura-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司经济学家的最新估计显示，特朗普总统禁止中国企业利用美国关税漏洞的决定将对中国数百亿美元的贸易造成冲击，并降低中国今年的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-banning-trade-loophole-will-cut-china-s-growth-nomura-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 04:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
